media: i2c: imx290: Add support for test pattern generation

Add support for generating following test patterns by IMX290:

* Sequence Pattern 1
* Horizontal Color-bar Chart
* Vertical Color-bar Chart
* Sequence Pattern 2
* Gradation Pattern 1
* Gradation Pattern 2
* 000/555h Toggle Pattern

